00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.220
and he wasn't interested
in baroque music at all.

00:08:04.220 --> 00:08:08.310
We were playing piano
trios together with Fauré

00:08:08.310 --> 00:08:11.360
and Beethoven and whatever.

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:13.530 position:56%
And I said, "Well, we can work,"
'cause I had already started playing

00:08:13.530 --> 00:08:16.370
with another colleague in my
1st year, playing harpsichord.

00:08:16.370 --> 00:08:18.040
And I said, "Play some
baroque violin,"

00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:19.340
he said, "I'm not interested.

00:08:19.340 --> 00:08:20.640
Not interested.

00:08:20.640 --> 00:08:21.940
I'm not interested in that."

00:08:21.940 --> 00:08:26.270
So I just put his name on a poster
