00:26:56.700 --> 00:27:00.210
It is the most colorful
area of Amsterdam,

00:27:00.210 --> 00:27:04.130 position:56%
and that is where Sweelinck
worked, and not, as you might think,

00:27:04.130 --> 00:27:06.430
playing for church services.

00:27:06.430 --> 00:27:10.080
