in both pieces.

00:27:54.530 --> 00:27:59.890
I'll say that again later
in the hall, but it's ...

00:27:59.890 --> 00:28:02.540
So there is definitely some
kind of cosmic connection.

00:28:02.540 --> 00:28:05.340
